OL,5, BBC chairman Richard Sharp made        
OL,6, "significant errors of judgement" in   
OL,7, acting as a go-between on a loan for   
OL,8, Boris Johnson while he was applying for
OL,9, the post, MPs have said.               
OL,11,FA cross-party committee said he had not
OL,12,Fgiven them the "full facts" two years  
OL,13,Fago when they were considering his     
OL,14,Fsuitability for the BBC role.          
OL,16,FHe should consider how this affected   
OL,17,Ftrust in him and the BBC, it said.     
OL,19,FMr Sharp apologised if MPs had not had 
OL,20,Fall the details they needed.           
